dct_title_s: Commercial ore deposits of Central Germany.
dct_description_sm: No relief shown. Includes sites where the following can be found: bituminous coal, brown coal, potash and rock salt, iron and manganese ore, copper-bearing shale outcrop, metallic ores (barite and fluorite), and petroleum. "No. A3047, 27 Jan. 1944." "Merseburg Atlas."
dct_creator_sm: United States. Office of Strategic Services
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C.] : Lithographed in the Reproduction Branch, 1944.
